Frequent washing of the skin can strip it of essential oils that protect the skin from irritations and infections. The Pigeon Wet Wipes with Chamomile will come in very handy to you especially while travelling as this will help you cleanse your infant’s and your skin. These Chamomile Wet Tissues from Pigeon are 100 per cent alcohol-free and hence is safe to be used on your tiny tot’s skin daily. It will not dry out the natural moisture of the infant’s gentle skin. These Pigeon Wet Tissues are microbiologically tested and ensured safe with no traces of bacteria or fungi in them. Made of thick and durable fabric that is soft these Pigeon Wet Wipes with Chamomile will help in wiping away dirt and clean your bundle of joy’s skin and gently moisturize it with the organic extracts of Chamomile. Pigeon Baby Wipes Chamomile and Rosehip Refill (82 Pieces) Price: Rs.225

Baby Wipes can be used to cleanse your infant’s skin without water and soap. The Pigeon Baby Wipes with Chamomile and Rosehip have been created to provide a safe and natural cleanser that every parent would desire for their little angels. Enriched with 100 per cent organic extracts of Chamomile and Rosehip that are certified by the USDA-NOP make this Wet wipe from Pigeon extremely skin friendly. These extracts infused into these Wipes provide a soothing relief to the skin and gives better hydration to dry skin.

The Rosehip extract that is rich in Vitamins like A
column16:

Made with purified water and 100 per cent free of alcohol\xa0the Pigeon Wet Wipes with Chamomile and Rosehip can be used on your bundle of joy’s tender skin every day. These extra soft tissues will brush gently against your little one’s skin and will not irritate her fragile skin in any way.
